    <h1>Rugged Thread Outerwear Repair</h1>
    <h2>Claim Ticket <%= @item.work_order.id %> - <%= @item.position %></h2>

    <h3><%= @item.brand %> <%= @item.item_type %></h3>
    <p>Estimate: <%= @item.estimate %></p>
    <p>Expected Completion Date: <%= @item.due_date %></p>
    <p>Please call or text if you haven't heard from us by the Expected Completion Date. We will always call or text when your repair is complete.</p>
    <p>Estimates are for budgeting purposes only. We will call or text for approval before proceeding if the repairs will exceed the estimate by more than 25%.</p>
